研究问题 1 每年最受欢迎的电影类别是哪些？¶

下方图中展示了历年最受欢迎电影类型的排行

In [180]:
# 用这个代码框和其它代码框探索数据。务必添加
#   Markdown 框，以便归档你的观察和调查结果。
genres = set()
# 提取出所有的电影类别
def addGenres(gs):
    splited = gs.split('|')
    for x in splited:
        genres.add(x)

movie_data['genres'].apply(addGenres)
years = np.sort(movie_data['release_year'].drop_duplicates().astype(str).values).tolist()
years.insert(0,'genres')
years

populars = pd.DataFrame(columns=years)
populars['genres'] = pd.Series(list(genres))
populars.fillna(0,inplace=True)

year_slice = years[1:]
for year in year_slice:
    counts = []
    for index,genre in enumerate(populars['genres']):
        genre_data = movie_data[movie_data['genres'].str.contains(genre)]
        genre_data.insert(loc=genre_data.shape[1],column='count',value=np.repeat(1,genre_data.shape[0]))
        count = genre_data[genre_data['release_year'] == int(year)]['count'].sum()
        counts.append(count)
    populars[year] = populars[year].add(pd.Series(counts))
# for year in year_slice:
    populars.sort_values(by=year,ascending=False).plot(x='genres',y=year,kind='bar',title="{}'s Popularity Rank Of Genres".format(year));

研究问题 2 票房高的电影有哪些特点？¶

票房最高的100部电影中，70%以上都含有冒险元素，50%以上都含有动作元素，40%以上都含有魔幻元素

In [183]:
popular_movies = movie_data.sort_values(by='revenue',ascending=False)[:100]

genres_revenue = pd.DataFrame(index=np.arange(len(genres)),columns=['genres','count'])
genres_revenue.fillna(0,inplace=True)
genres = list(genres)
genres_revenue['genres'] = pd.Series(genres)
genres_revenue
counts = np.repeat(0.0,len(genres))
for index,genre in enumerate(genres):
    for gs in popular_movies['genres']:
        if genre in gs:
            counts[index] += 1
genres_revenue['count'] = pd.Series(counts).apply(lambda x : x / popular_movies.shape[0])
genres_revenue.sort_values(by='count',ascending=False,inplace=True)
genres_revenue.plot(kind='bar',x='genres',y='count',title='The Most Popular Movie\'s Genres');
